t green city in 2035\n- Explore a future path by experiencing a space for carbon neutrality\n- Learn about the need for carbon neutrality and what young people can do\n- Learn about core underlying technologies such as realistic content technology provided as an experience\n\n2. Characteristics of content\n- First-person perspective in which the experiencer becomes the main character\n- 7-step composition according to the actual experience process\n- Developed based on standing only\n- Movement and manipulation using the Oculus Controller\n- Estimated experience time of about 20 to 30 minutes\n\n3. 7-step configuration\nSTEP 1 Instructions on how to operate\nSTEP 2 Meeting with the UN Youth Delegation\nSTEP 3 Practicing carbon neutrality in urban forests\nSTEP 4 Implementation of carbon neutrality in wind power plants\nSTEP 5 Carbon neutrality practice at the East Coast carbon storage site\nSTEP 6 Think\nSTEP 7 Finishing\n", "short_description": "It is a VR content that allows teenagers to experience a space for carbon neutrality, learn about the need for carbon neutrality, what they can do, and explore future career paths."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "HeroCover_3000x900.png", "id": "7527653000591853", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001730_7527653007258519_8435369833685824333_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ApQ-GZMUkzIQ7kNvgGJRlVQ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDG1P49eDSIXjch_JhyPFNQL8d2XqWg6qp_7cgXqjAlYA&oe=67727282"}, {"file_name": "Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1452940842279363", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031355_1452940845612696_1891464877969558457_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_QnY8yzqbgcQ7kNvgExIfFb&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sjc3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDJNu9EG19wKJ4tDR1yyotrpWHrF2N-sA1oKViwxn2soA&oe=67729144"}, {"file_name": "Portrait_1008x1440.png", "id